{"tid":1502652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［賽後檢討］好唔抵、好傷心、又有手足被捉","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:17:34.000Z","uid":23830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30e6e45d7b9fde6e260a47a118fbe7a4c712bcbe","tid":1502652,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"今日戰果係咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n損失了十多位前線男女，一隻眼，胸骨射斷，再兩人中彈傷。<br />\n<br />\n成日只係俾咗刺激俾香港人而矣！實際係輸了一仗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，啱啱喺彩虹時，見到三隻落單POPO，在站內暗道，狹路相逢，卻被POPO趕出來關門，喂，成幾百人怕三隻狗？我地太善良了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n委實要再研究地區戰戰法再是否有效，同埋有咩壓力俾到政府。<br />\n<br />\n大家。前線（武武）又好後援（非非）又好，我地為被捉嘅手足集氣希望佢地平安，亦等我地亦好好希望、好好再思考黎緊嘅安排。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共勉。"},{"pid":"c5f354abaf675fdaf727b8fca4493384806eb63d","tid":1502652,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09d96f6ef58bbf52d08f6c8b3e51cc7403ac5d79","tid":1502652,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f24964b7d362902e0f57cf74871c51ff1541fd04","tid":1502652,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"2 個月 0 戰術突破"},{"pid":"4e1ceb860cee2271558fc81e805302fac09da6f8","tid":1502652,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:02:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af21acc1bae2664ae0dd2aa31e646fbfdeb59f0c","tid":1502652,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"【戰術】今日荃灣同往後戰術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[屌醒勇武] 不進，則退<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502160</a><br />\n- 分享自 L